  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installation of Inkscape</title>

    <para>
      Install <application>Inkscape</application> by running the following
      commands:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>sed -r "s:.*(unsigned GC_version).*:\1 = GC_get_version()\;:" \
    -i configure &amp;&amp;

sed -e "s|GfxColorSpace::parse(|&amp;NULL, |g" \
    -i src/extension/internal/pdfinput/pdf-parser.cpp &amp;&amp;

./configure --prefix=/usr &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      This package does not have a working testsuite.
    </para>

    <para>
      Now, as the <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem> user:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>

    <xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"
      href="../../xincludes/update-icons-and-desktop.xml"/>

  </sect2>

  <sect2 role="commands">
    <title>Command Explanations</title>

    <para>
      <command>sed ... -i ...</command>: The first <command>sed</command> fixes
      building with GC-7.4 and later and the second <command>sed</command>
      fixes building with Poppler-0.29.0 and later.
    </para>

  </sect2>

